{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-437","title":"犯罪入狱","sectionId":"chapter-20","sectionTitle":"依法办事不出错","pageStart":2151,"pageEnd":2155,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":10,"duplicateEntryCount":24,"pages":[{"number":2151,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"437 犯罪入狱"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"behind bars 监狱服刑","headword":"behind bars"},{"type":"entry","text":"concertina wire 铁丝网","headword":"concertina wire"}]},{"number":2152,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"guard tower 守卫塔，警戒塔","headword":"guard tower"},{"type":"entry","text":"security lighting 警卫照明","headword":"security lighting"}]},{"number":2153,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"prison uniform 狱服，囚衣","headword":"prison uniform"}]},{"number":2154,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"crime rate 犯罪率","headword":"crime rate"},{"type":"entry","text":"criminal organisation 犯罪组织","headword":"criminal organisation"},{"type":"entry","text":"visit a prisoner 探监","headword":"visit a prisoner"},{"type":"entry","text":"prison breach 越狱","headword":"prison breach"},{"type":"entry","text":"escape from jail 从监狱中逃走","headword":"escape from jail"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Do you know the final determination of the case? （你知道这个"},{"type":"text","text":"案子的最终裁定吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：The man is facing up to ten years in prison. （这个男人面临长达"},{"type":"text","text":"十年的牢狱生活）。"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"}]},{"number":2155,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：Do you know why the criminal can escape from jail? （你知道罪"},{"type":"text","text":"犯为什么能从监狱中逃走吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Because the warden was out of responsibility. （因为监狱长失职"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I heard he committed a crime. （我听说他犯罪了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yes, and he is behind bars now. （是的，他现在正在监狱服"},{"type":"text","text":"刑。）"}]}]}